ygData.messageBody:
Greetings everyone! =)

I just wanted to introduce myself. I am Jax Elysium (or Jaxy) who
originated from Qeynos in the land of Karana, but recently have had a
change of heart and a sort of metamorphisis to an extremely sad and
lonely child of Innoruk on Vallon Zek.

I don't quite understand, but realize that sometimes the Gods dont'
explain why or what they do when they play with their mortal children.

I was hoping to find someone on this list who also serves the will of
the Dark Lord who would say Hi or something on Vallon Zek.

Ooc: otherwise I'm a 29 year old newlywed! (got married July 1st) and
my husband and I met on meridian59 two years ago and are extremely
happy! Only problem is that we only have one computer, so we don't get
a chance to explore and play together =((
But we still watch each other play and we both love EQ!

anyways just wanted to introduce myself to y'all!!

Jaxy (Jennifer)
